description:

Our custom color prices are for all 3 bundles

name: Virgin Hair Deep Conditioner Treatment
description:
Before we ship your virgin hair to you we do offer a Deep Conditioner Treatment on ALL Hair. If you would like your hair Deep Conditioned than please add a extra two days to your hair delivery.

This deep conditioner is a treatment for all virgin hair that will hydrate your hair and leave it with a glamourous shine and a nice silky feel. We definitley recommend our Deep Conditioner Treatment.

We Treat and Deep Condition all bundles
